<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/27505195">中国古代有哪些有倾城之姿却不太出名的美女？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3184870" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">不出名指的是大部分人都不太了解的古代美女，，我今天刚知道的郑旦算一个，还有么</div>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-meta zm-item-comment-el clearfix" id="zh-question-meta-wrap">
<div class="zm-meta-panel">

